On 7/18/05 9:47 AM, "Darren Evans-Young" <darren(-at-)bama.ua.edu> wrote:

> I'm getting around to lubing my bus and discovered that I'm missing
> one of the zerk fittings. What size fitting should I get to replace it?
> Can I get these at a FLAPS?

Sometimes: they are metric. These are the part number for the 5 zerks.

N 018 515 1 front center
N 018 516 1 top beam (90 deg.) x2
N 018 511 2 bottom beam (straight) x2

I've bought them from the dealer before so you might try Bus Depot.

